Rocky ?

199
00:31:47.043 --> 00:31:48.441
Ici mon garçon.

200
00:31:53.582 --> 00:31:55.598
Allez, Rocky.

201
00:31:57.186 --> 00:31:59.235
Je vais juste chercher Rocky.

202
00:32:01.056 --> 00:32:02.738
Rocky.

