383
01:04:50.724 --> 01:04:53.787
- Cours !
- Zooey, allez !


384
01:06:29.623 --> 01:06:33.093
Non. Non. Non.

385
01:06:33.493 --> 01:06:35.122
Non !

386
01:06:35.395 --> 01:06:37.064
Non !

